{
  "version": "1",
  "questId": "fr_08",
  "lang": "uk",
  "lines": [
    {
      "key": "000fc05",
      "nodeTitle": "item_hat",
      "sourceText": "Тепла шапка зігріє вашу голову.",
      "sourceEnText": "A warm hat keeps your head warm.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_000fc05.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2482,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:41:08Z",
      "textHash": "2bda21e7e2e8bf9368fe04c3ddbdad489aa290fb7694ae032f44ae01b5ffe872"
    },
    {
      "key": "001e940",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base4",
      "sourceText": "Давайте відповімо на три гірські запитання перед грою з прапорами.",
      "sourceEnText": "Let's answer three mountain questions before the flag game.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_001e940.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 4389,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T16:42:26Z",
      "textHash": "3b41697ab0050f506eb84328eaa2c8cf5e15069ceb038266d1e457eeb9c19979"
    },
    {
      "key": "003e87c",
      "nodeTitle": "chest_bonus",
      "sourceText": "Ти знайшов теплий шарф!",
      "sourceEnText": "You found a warm scarf!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_003e87c.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 1881,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:41:53Z",
      "textHash": "1bfceffd8a0a6ad5f98b87345deda4fe62822aa9c435034b4460993b98c701b4"
    },
    {
      "key": "003ecb2",
      "nodeTitle": "spawned_tourist",
      "sourceText": "Монблан — найвища гора в Альпах!",
      "sourceEnText": "Mont Blanc is the highest mountain in the Alps!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_003ecb2.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "ADULT_F",
      "durationMs": 3448,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:41:55Z",
      "textHash": "5469aac1016c94bc5f8e8a133c95f276ff4fc55b6700492f14e994207c8e64e5"
    },
    {
      "key": "00a7e83",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base3",
      "sourceText": "Правильно! Використовуйте їх, щоб залишатися на місці.",
      "sourceEnText": "Correct! Use them to stay steady.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_00a7e83.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 4153,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:41:23Z",
      "textHash": "7d8c3a0f75789a062b92dc412712dc6fa37cf20c716eb981020fe4d10c8cc204"
    },
    {
      "key": "011dc7e",
      "nodeTitle": "spawned_tourist",
      "sourceText": "Я люблю гори!",
      "sourceEnText": "I love the mountains!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_011dc7e.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "ADULT_F",
      "durationMs": 1515,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:41:54Z",
      "textHash": "7c66eff05009a98cbba888ef6b38fae22d73cb9d9295c8bee2f383b0bb925eeb"
    },
    {
      "key": "015bf8a",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base1",
      "sourceText": "Тепер ви готові до сходження!",
      "sourceEnText": "You are now ready to climb!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_015bf8a.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2429,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:41:01Z",
      "textHash": "259c48da7c8ada85fcda76946eca031d2c2f0e23ea6e3435e6e3f1c59ee28c75"
    },
    {
      "key": "018880a",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base4",
      "sourceText": "Ця вершина має висоту 4807 метрів.",
      "sourceEnText": "This summit is 4807 meters high.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_018880a.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 3553,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:41:29Z",
      "textHash": "510d676ae21d491cace2289064eb938827cab226962815c6841e59c3f69af445"
    },
    {
      "key": "01a4b20",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base3",
      "sourceText": "Ласти",
      "sourceEnText": "Flippers",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_01a4b20.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 862,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:41:24Z",
      "textHash": "e82ef0492fdf493041e8a0311999f62444d064c12d48d9c4724c4d0368e433d8"
    },
    {
      "key": "01beb5e",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_intro",
      "sourceText": "Ми бачили, як собака біг на гору.",
      "sourceEnText": "We saw the dog run up the mountain.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_01beb5e.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2612,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:40:55Z",
      "textHash": "091b1c855c28f15ac04cb871f3092b396df867231909bd6f577938b78b85e654"
    },
    {
      "key": "01e5f66",
      "nodeTitle": "spawned_hiker",
      "sourceText": "Той льодовик схожий на замерзлу річку.",
      "sourceEnText": "That glacier looks like a frozen river.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_01e5f66.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "ADULT_M",
      "durationMs": 2769,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:42:01Z",
      "textHash": "b141a849674167eeb7d3ac8e789f29bbec7eab981a1458c07e2b99f0b41990de"
    },
    {
      "key": "029a03e",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base2",
      "sourceText": "Сонце на снігу дуже яскраве. Нам потрібен захист для очей.",
      "sourceEnText": "The sun on the snow is very bright. We need eye protection.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_029a03e.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 4206,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:41:12Z",
      "textHash": "9867936f846852ced6a91e1b243edefd8a91cce8d280554557ae8f38b8c642e0"
    },
    {
      "key": "029f39c",
      "nodeTitle": "item_backpack",
      "sourceText": "Тепер ми можемо вийти з базового табору та розпочати пригоду!",
      "sourceEnText": "Now we can exit the base camp and start the adventure!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_029f39c.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 4336,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:41:01Z",
      "textHash": "55506409276aab26e2466a23e7bf0d2e8a8d216fbc71a47ce73a55f82a3ecf19"
    },
    {
      "key": "02a2ea9",
      "nodeTitle": "item_sunglasses",
      "sourceText": "Сніг і лід відбивають яскраве сонячне світло.",
      "sourceEnText": "Snow and ice reflect bright sunlight.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_02a2ea9.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 4153,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:41:18Z",
      "textHash": "eb568550aa11526ad68bcf0cbbb48a46a44d1d77a9c427e60765ba798a39aab3"
    },
    {
      "key": "02a3874",
      "nodeTitle": "snowman",
      "sourceText": "Ні, я залишаюся тут.",
      "sourceEnText": "No, I stay here",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_02a3874.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2299,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:41:49Z",
      "textHash": "4d25ec5e1de98e01d877ee2dfbee0a305e5f8de5c7bb5ce50a4d64f25e34a05f"
    },
    {
      "key": "02c9805",
      "nodeTitle": "activity_3_done",
      "sourceText": "Відкрий скриню, щоб дістати кішки!",
      "sourceEnText": "Open the chest to get crampons!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_02c9805.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2429,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:41:26Z",
      "textHash": "815430719b65ae99e2b767ce69ababaf3afc0f61168e5ebba7bfe389cd0b9e5a"
    },
    {
      "key": "030fa1c",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base4",
      "sourceText": "Ви впоралися! Ми на вершині Монблану.",
      "sourceEnText": "You made it! We are at the top of Mont Blanc.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_030fa1c.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 3213,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:41:28Z",
      "textHash": "263647268b25f3a4b5c443167503d2c8b66e01b0de3c0dd7bb32bc68ef1f4a17"
    },
    {
      "key": "035e68a",
      "nodeTitle": "snowman",
      "sourceText": "Базовий табір 4",
      "sourceEnText": "Basecamp 4",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_035e68a.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 1881,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:41:48Z",
      "textHash": "819f7231d15487a5c337d5b278ef8af817404c2e0859eb1b80aa380066f6c42c"
    },
    {
      "key": "0371d31",
      "nodeTitle": "spawned_alps_climber",
      "sourceText": "Сходження з гідом безпечніше.",
      "sourceEnText": "Climbing with a guide is safer.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_0371d31.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "ADULT_F",
      "durationMs": 2534,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:42:03Z",
      "textHash": "dfe353513b8a7fa00cf32ffab23b0362b2b850f279f7f755f859ca8c2c03d933"
    },
    {
      "key": "038d1bc",
      "nodeTitle": "item_rope",
      "sourceText": "Мотузка допомагає альпіністам залишатися в безпеці на льоду та скелях.",
      "sourceEnText": "The rope helps climbers stay safe on ice and rock.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_038d1bc.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 4989,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:41:27Z",
      "textHash": "87f95318f897a3fa9a99a104b4917e97a32a44b9ee6004e384c0b7198259df35"
    },
    {
      "key": "03db010",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_swiss",
      "sourceText": "Швейцарія розташована на північ від Монблану.",
      "sourceEnText": "Switzerland is north of Mont Blanc.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_03db010.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 4571,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T16:42:28Z",
      "textHash": "c7639b719dbfc658ed40502e41734c6ad31031c4176ba1c9eaf8bbb9045dd1b3"
    },
    {
      "key": "03dd802",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base1",
      "sourceText": "Тобі не вистачає пальто!",
      "sourceEnText": "You are missing the coat!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_03dd802.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 1933,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:41:03Z",
      "textHash": "c91a35f94ae1b4a9d2592726609830da9cbb9c7ccdca0528b2a9184de9d814ae"
    },
    {
      "key": "045409f",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_intro",
      "sourceText": "Перш ніж вирушати, вам знадобиться рюкзак.",
      "sourceEnText": "Before going, you need a backpack.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_045409f.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2900,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:40:57Z",
      "textHash": "38f5795ffa0966b39bdcc73e669c681ad8b7bcfe5d338a2d0b14a371fb7e45a8"
    },
    {
      "key": "046eb33",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_intro",
      "sourceText": "Повернися, коли закінчиш завдання.",
      "sourceEnText": "Come back when you finish the task.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_046eb33.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2978,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:40:53Z",
      "textHash": "298fd39460fd2e8046ec245a4f204d1d3576665531c6291141a0f4a73a722741"
    },
    {
      "key": "04bbada",
      "nodeTitle": "spawned_tourist",
      "sourceText": "Сподіваюся побачити бабака!",
      "sourceEnText": "I hope to see a marmot!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_04bbada.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "ADULT_F",
      "durationMs": 2116,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:41:56Z",
      "textHash": "1415beda89cd49d18f8904777d85d261227b34b07a6e156346b7f66be7ae59af"
    },
    {
      "key": "04c1c1f",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_intro",
      "sourceText": "Бачу, у тебе є рюкзак. Тепер можеш йти!",
      "sourceEnText": "I see you have the backpack. Now you can go!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_04c1c1f.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 3448,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:40:50Z",
      "textHash": "cb56d2d52aadae95a4ac87cf6f4ecea313e4f4bb297ef957e178f68cfd92c9e3"
    },
    {
      "key": "050fe70",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_italy",
      "sourceText": "Італія розташована на схід від Монблану.",
      "sourceEnText": "Italy is east of Mont Blanc.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_050fe70.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2978,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T16:42:27Z",
      "textHash": "90e2958172c766c321f67eb5ad8d3f448eaff97bd2185c2659e0550e6cf30ebf"
    },
    {
      "key": "0557ef5",
      "nodeTitle": "spawned_hiker",
      "sourceText": "Вітер може швидко змінюватися.",
      "sourceEnText": "The wind can change fast.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_0557ef5.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "ADULT_M",
      "durationMs": 2429,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:41:59Z",
      "textHash": "9d2d46feb0cd08f80a0896d00a1e04bc9240d96516554a0b325eeda631ec60e1"
    },
    {
      "key": "056ec2b",
      "nodeTitle": "chest_base1",
      "sourceText": "Відкривається! Там є деяке обладнання.",
      "sourceEnText": "It opens! It contains some equipment.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_056ec2b.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 3082,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:41:06Z",
      "textHash": "cddf9452702c1da11782f190933e2d4905c56eb8ff2f9bbc4c8d8c6690cefeee"
    },
    {
      "key": "058bb65",
      "nodeTitle": "snowman",
      "sourceText": "Базовий табір 3",
      "sourceEnText": "Basecamp 3",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_058bb65.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 1411,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:41:47Z",
      "textHash": "79a6fe7f1328c46bccd7c992df5b06e6b127171a5d5e328a68ee0ab51d2cfde6"
    },
    {
      "key": "0590129",
      "nodeTitle": "spawned_tourist",
      "sourceText": "Не забудьте взяти теплий одяг!",
      "sourceEnText": "Don't forget to bring warm clothes!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_0590129.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "ADULT_F",
      "durationMs": 2194,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:41:57Z",
      "textHash": "3f53c511d290e12019256e40245193269c6199383e7c04a442f576032e98945d"
    },
    {
      "key": "059d744",
      "nodeTitle": "item_hat",
      "sourceText": "Це також допомагає, коли дме холодний вітер.",
      "sourceEnText": "It also helps when the wind is cold.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_059d744.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 3030,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:41:08Z",
      "textHash": "9634e2960a76e47d6e84b3a749ef1437c2e4a59826a42b08351d2389d5dbb1d3"
    },
    {
      "key": "05cabb5",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_intro",
      "sourceText": "Шукай навколо!",
      "sourceEnText": "Look around for it!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_05cabb5.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 1463,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:40:57Z",
      "textHash": "a6a3d4c63232edaab232add6bda28023aa48653aae0dc28f2d75ce55685a1755"
    },
    {
      "key": "05e3658",
      "nodeTitle": "snowman",
      "sourceText": "Базовий табір 2",
      "sourceEnText": "Basecamp 2",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_05e3658.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 1411,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:41:47Z",
      "textHash": "de4476ee0165249614541761f3e53d93440d490b5853bae536d99a49232eb59a"
    },
    {
      "key": "05e80cb",
      "nodeTitle": "item_backpack",
      "sourceText": "Цей рюкзак може містити їжу, воду та карту.",
      "sourceEnText": "This backpack can carry food, water, and a map.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_05e80cb.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 3448,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:41:00Z",
      "textHash": "cec7060764f75c4a66f046dc774e9d244e19534bec945010f8e69bf13d3acd93"
    },
    {
      "key": "0650acc",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_intro",
      "sourceText": "Будь ласка, дослідіть Монблан та знайдіть наше спорядження.",
      "sourceEnText": "Please explore Mont Blanc and find our gear.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_0650acc.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 4284,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:40:56Z",
      "textHash": "32573a893dc84ab28dfd7823b5abc12fcf388861a4df18ccea50d75e5a7a7a52"
    },
    {
      "key": "06b15bb",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base3",
      "sourceText": "У вас є льодове спорядження. Останній поштовх до вершини!",
      "sourceEnText": "You have the ice gear. One last push to the top!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_06b15bb.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 4232,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:41:19Z",
      "textHash": "150eb12d70947a617c8df6f5ec39f1468ab6b321e67ba8b9b3b843ff352fa45f"
    },
    {
      "key": "06b3363",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base2",
      "sourceText": "Тобі бракує рукавичок!",
      "sourceEnText": "You are missing the gloves!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_06b3363.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2116,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:41:11Z",
      "textHash": "4dc2705cb27b77e7036063829bd32602e1358981083591b847e6a84e15e3577a"
    },
    {
      "key": "06d9f34",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base3",
      "sourceText": "Щоб ходити по льодовиковому льоду, нам потрібне спеціальне спорядження.",
      "sourceEnText": "To walk on glacier ice, we need special gear.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_06d9f34.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 4937,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:41:21Z",
      "textHash": "12fb2fbdd5ed91848efd3d5cae5aaf8462e633d4c23380adec0c6e5be09c3de9"
    },
    {
      "key": "06f9a2a",
      "nodeTitle": "question_alps",
      "sourceText": "У якому гірському хребті знаходиться Монблан?",
      "sourceEnText": "What mountain range is Mont Blanc in?",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_06f9a2a.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 3370,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:41:31Z",
      "textHash": "6eeef78d6e1fec0c4b1f6612e9e7bd9fff5fffc494a2a4adf8f8a24aeef46236"
    },
    {
      "key": "07102e7",
      "nodeTitle": "item_crampons",
      "sourceText": "Вони допоможуть вам безпечно ходити по льоду.",
      "sourceEnText": "These help you walk safely on ice.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_07102e7.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 3265,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:41:27Z",
      "textHash": "ba5c78e4a719f2ea0dd17a475b812675cbc2c764ef6e7bb2332981143657ed02"
    },
    {
      "key": "0724de3",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_intro",
      "sourceText": "Допоможіть! Я гірський гід. Синій собака забрав наше альпіністське спорядження!",
      "sourceEnText": "Help! I am a mountain guide. A blue dog took our climbing gear!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_0724de3.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 6740,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:40:54Z",
      "textHash": "f5579e148e91a831c996bf27012dc9eafbc054da2324f24762b6f1075a00ad6c"
    },
    {
      "key": "076433f",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base3",
      "sourceText": "Що одягати на черевики, щоб ходити по льоду і не ковзати?",
      "sourceEnText": "What do you put on your boots to walk on ice and not slip?",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_076433f.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 4049,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:41:22Z",
      "textHash": "6fe7c1d4d1f0c25e770a04304502c76744aa25501302b7deedc469cdb7af7d50"
    },
    {
      "key": "07c6385",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base3",
      "sourceText": "Ні! Ти не плаваєш! Спробуй ще раз.",
      "sourceEnText": "No! You aren't swimming! Try again.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_07c6385.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 3187,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:41:25Z",
      "textHash": "8a270b9e56c4c5bc5b4c16b30494e293fb8a0ca6bc728d8b642e29df2966b8bb"
    },
    {
      "key": "07f2635",
      "nodeTitle": "snowman",
      "sourceText": "Базовий табір 1",
      "sourceEnText": "Basecamp 1",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_07f2635.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 1646,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:41:46Z",
      "textHash": "2930cf76a87da03492c770211d9a3a35051ce17426feb5dda32cd78c6f3f754b"
    },
    {
      "key": "07f2699",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_intro",
      "sourceText": "Знайдіть усе спорядження для скелелазіння та дізнайтеся про три сусідні країни!",
      "sourceEnText": "Find all the climbing gear and learn about the three nearby countries!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_07f2699.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 5904,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T16:42:24Z",
      "textHash": "bc05906732231cf9ab5ea4ce1f58945b16b71915acf456d91437cf96957a570e"
    },
    {
      "key": "0809dce",
      "nodeTitle": "spawned_alps_climber",
      "sourceText": "Я люблю скелелазіння в Альпах.",
      "sourceEnText": "I love climbing in the Alps.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_0809dce.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "ADULT_F",
      "durationMs": 2142,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:42:01Z",
      "textHash": "e61fc62a683810caf6fe652fa06587cb0effef0917922c35f9a2707cd35bd0ca"
    },
    {
      "key": "081fbe4",
      "nodeTitle": "spawned_alps_climber",
      "sourceText": "Кішки допомагають мені ходити по твердому льоду.",
      "sourceEnText": "Crampons help me walk on hard ice.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_081fbe4.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "ADULT_F",
      "durationMs": 3213,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:42:02Z",
      "textHash": "cb66381ad1bd6d68fc3908112be93060407c75c9268c6e7052138203e161d811"
    },
    {
      "key": "088fb7f",
      "nodeTitle": "item_sunglasses",
      "sourceText": "Сонячні окуляри захищають ваші очі.",
      "sourceEnText": "Sunglasses protect your eyes.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_088fb7f.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2900,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:41:18Z",
      "textHash": "5d347a9436b7b37c8943444d3c18a2fd2e9f552eb83c3766313e45908bc0e9fa"
    },
    {
      "key": "097ecf0",
      "nodeTitle": "spawned_tourist",
      "sourceText": "Гори можуть бути небезпечними, тож будьте обережні!",
      "sourceEnText": "Mountains can be dangerous, so be careful!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_097ecf0.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "ADULT_F",
      "durationMs": 3500,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T16:42:29Z",
      "textHash": "71bd4165fbfaa03c7e85e4db863054e6212d8dec5bc22986c79a6236df40c98d"
    },
    {
      "key": "0a70f7d",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base2",
      "sourceText": "Що захищає ваші очі від яскравого снігу та сонця?",
      "sourceEnText": "What protects your eyes from bright snow and sun?",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_0a70f7d.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 4441,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T16:42:25Z",
      "textHash": "f678dbf75aca0aa38842c49f0a5deda5c50a6c61fcb66e0e907a39c9c8b8d2c0"
    },
    {
      "key": "0a7146f",
      "nodeTitle": "item_hat",
      "sourceText": "Тепер можна продовжувати підйом!",
      "sourceEnText": "Now you can continue the climb!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_0a7146f.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2351,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:41:09Z",
      "textHash": "9e7d08cbb38597f31a43b4f248b4237391a71b7223da8babd0fbb1931f13e6d7"
    },
    {
      "key": "0afb2dc",
      "nodeTitle": "item_scarf",
      "sourceText": "Шарф блокує вітер на вашій шиї.",
      "sourceEnText": "A scarf blocks wind on your neck.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_0afb2dc.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2847,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:41:54Z",
      "textHash": "204b70cf75c9d6985e07a81ef0b2104ee0bc5d16d083d261ba1b7198c62c6ff3"
    },
    {
      "key": "0b50050",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base3",
      "sourceText": "Крампони",
      "sourceEnText": "Crampons",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_0b50050.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 1097,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:41:23Z",
      "textHash": "f2ddf387e3325a46f569b7f01a73deabc8207d1f10542ce99907d628059499b3"
    },
    {
      "key": "0bc67f7",
      "nodeTitle": "spawned_hiker",
      "sourceText": "Я йду по мотузці, коли ожеледиця.",
      "sourceEnText": "I follow the rope line when it is icy.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_0bc67f7.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "ADULT_M",
      "durationMs": 2482,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:42:00Z",
      "textHash": "b8053aeeb0db8b4d90a7717d0cbf4609f12aec3d21438dd4d5f299095aafe88e"
    },
    {
      "key": "0c18060",
      "nodeTitle": "snowman",
      "sourceText": "Тобі потрібна допомога, щоб піднятися на гору?",
      "sourceEnText": "Do you need help to climb the mountain?",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_0c18060.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 3082,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:41:45Z",
      "textHash": "5a675ac253c11f9c92938d7f71008e4be36d26ea6ef9d7ef32ffbccd8575e208"
    },
    {
      "key": "0c18c08",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base3",
      "sourceText": "Тобі бракує мотузки!",
      "sourceEnText": "You are missing the rope!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_0c18c08.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2011,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:41:20Z",
      "textHash": "841811d39e06b9625d327a4577007354e7d4f5cd2205d414f7ba7ea108fa5157"
    },
    {
      "key": "0c1f006",
      "nodeTitle": "chest_intro",
      "sourceText": "Відкривається! У ньому рюкзак.",
      "sourceEnText": "It opens! It contains a backpack.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_0c1f006.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2377,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:40:58Z",
      "textHash": "43a7b4c10922138079d5be6647d1bc0746b4ea88e3be2b6a62b553722bdd04f7"
    },
    {
      "key": "0d01879",
      "nodeTitle": "item_gloves",
      "sourceText": "Холодні руки ускладнюють скелелазіння.",
      "sourceEnText": "Cold hands make climbing hard.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_0d01879.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 3187,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:41:17Z",
      "textHash": "ea6a5f64c1467494c0d45102cb4a81b55a5a7301b11dc734a1045e63eeff3bb2"
    },
    {
      "key": "0d23529",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_france",
      "sourceText": "Франція знаходиться на захід від Монблану.",
      "sourceEnText": "France is west of Mont Blanc.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_0d23529.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2900,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T16:42:27Z",
      "textHash": "12fc97c0fbdf381bf94b4d665b446dca6d2a9df1c653bd6105eb2d3805fda9cc"
    },
    {
      "key": "0dbac73",
      "nodeTitle": "spawned_hiker",
      "sourceText": "Для походів тут потрібні гарні черевики.",
      "sourceEnText": "Hiking here needs good boots.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_0dbac73.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "ADULT_M",
      "durationMs": 3030,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:41:58Z",
      "textHash": "487922bb5a4411c2540b6f2cdc3d18dd9088ed51df0ae09cee8d5a532be3b069"
    },
    {
      "key": "0e23f1f",
      "nodeTitle": "item_coat",
      "sourceText": "Це пальто зігріє вас у вітер та сніг.",
      "sourceEnText": "This coat keeps you warm in wind and snow.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_0e23f1f.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2952,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:41:07Z",
      "textHash": "0fa300ac8f9aec68874a00d2abd50e7500d35fec70002a259b8f591769cc166f"
    },
    {
      "key": "0e83480",
      "nodeTitle": "activity_1_done",
      "sourceText": "Відкрий скриню, щоб дістати теплу шапку!",
      "sourceEnText": "Open the chest to get a warm hat!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_0e83480.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2978,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:41:05Z",
      "textHash": "0f75e380062ef3a70560c3d4a49c8fa0041b453649a7806b595b5b2e8e046bf0"
    },
    {
      "key": "0f2aac7",
      "nodeTitle": "item_gloves",
      "sourceText": "Рукавички зберігають пальці теплими та сухими.",
      "sourceEnText": "Gloves keep fingers warm and dry.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_0f2aac7.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 3448,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:41:16Z",
      "textHash": "308d02e0c0ae056dd49c928a4d8c6b8a30ea14f047fab5b35d572141e0fbfa1a"
    },
    {
      "key": "0f4644b",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_intro",
      "sourceText": "Давайте піднімемося на Монблан.",
      "sourceEnText": "Let's climb Mont Blanc.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_0f4644b.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2247,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:40:51Z",
      "textHash": "080c85acc120c7638bcec9904545da31dc4ce377308bde5b84bb6e9afa6bffae"
    },
    {
      "key": "0f4c405",
      "nodeTitle": "snowman",
      "sourceText": "Так",
      "sourceEnText": "Yes",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_0f4c405.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 627,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:41:45Z",
      "textHash": "8f38a7f1ad9d6dcdb52f9d4d3fcc35cda3da6ed6af51aa7e6d918b188b78e826"
    },
    {
      "key": "0fdc3cb",
      "nodeTitle": "activity_2_done",
      "sourceText": "Відкрий скриню, щоб дістати сонцезахисні окуляри!",
      "sourceEnText": "Open the chest to get sunglasses!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_0fdc3cb.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 3631,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:41:14Z",
      "textHash": "90d0b7362181d020c594dbf409d4b87bb253f7ceb5a29e3bbd39896bca4c6401"
    },
    {
      "key": "b1_1",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base1",
      "sourceText": "Вітер починає дути. Мої вуха потребують захисту!",
      "sourceEnText": "The wind is starting to blow. My ears need protection!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_b1_1.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 4049,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:41:04Z",
      "textHash": "3062a4ceb0b6a89193e98335ef59726adcea357e6d3de85cbeaed5b29e919657"
    },
    {
      "key": "b1_q",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base1",
      "sourceText": "Як захистити вуха, коли сильний вітер?",
      "sourceEnText": "How do we protect the ears when the wind is strong?",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_b1_q.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2560,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:41:05Z",
      "textHash": "d236a1e791fbb5bebe7ef8672e00493a15e6fa0b126efca611cec30587d68af2"
    },
    {
      "key": "chest_locked",
      "nodeTitle": "chest_intro",
      "sourceText": "Воно замкнене. Можливо, тобі потрібен ключ.",
      "sourceEnText": "It's locked. Maybe you need a key.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_chest_locked.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 3683,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:40:59Z",
      "textHash": "5f33ca8f83f25c1911d88fddedf1c0608c73538ff6aa2d3892aac931f55c865a"
    },
    {
      "key": "comebacklater",
      "nodeTitle": "question_alps",
      "sourceText": "Повертайся пізніше!",
      "sourceEnText": "Come back later!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_comebacklater.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 1933,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T18:59:06Z",
      "textHash": "2e76eb8d2429b78ff34998ed321d74109dc99fa11d8eb7fcac3a8c14ac95b74c"
    },
    {
      "key": "correct",
      "nodeTitle": "question_alps",
      "sourceText": "Правильно!",
      "sourceEnText": "Correct!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_correct.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 993,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:41:32Z",
      "textHash": "f3350b043e4ec0d61df3c37eabb0f5ed20c5a9e19c5c4f7981603b5f06fd846a"
    },
    {
      "key": "dontknow",
      "nodeTitle": "question_alps",
      "sourceText": "Я не знаю",
      "sourceEnText": "I don't know",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_dontknow.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 993,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T18:59:06Z",
      "textHash": "ef74e6f6b807789e4d654b5ef26ab477466adfb2225141d4946753d58fb88cf6"
    },
    {
      "key": "end_1",
      "nodeTitle": "quest_end",
      "sourceText": "Неймовірно! Ви досягли вершини Монблану. Його висота 4807 метрів!",
      "sourceEnText": "Amazing! You reached the top of Mont Blanc. It is 4807 meters high!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_end_1.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 6374,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:40:48Z",
      "textHash": "cd60e57c3d6ae547ae0b13ecb0c95f4252d9cd34460c7a661ada5fa1d9ad0dda"
    },
    {
      "key": "end_2",
      "nodeTitle": "quest_end",
      "sourceText": "Альпи повні високих, красивих гір.",
      "sourceEnText": "The Alps are full of tall, beautiful mountains.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_end_2.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2978,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:40:49Z",
      "textHash": "60b2a33f8b269890f590799a693d3f12b53fe86b64179733b3c0649434a16dc0"
    },
    {
      "key": "fr08_b2_chest",
      "nodeTitle": "chest_base2",
      "sourceText": "Відкривається! Всередині є сонцезахисні окуляри.",
      "sourceEnText": "It opens! It has sunglasses inside.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_fr08_b2_chest.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 4049,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:41:15Z",
      "textHash": "c64e80a05fc46dca02547308f73bd490bc732e0bfcb823ce3df920bbdd5ab0c7"
    },
    {
      "key": "fr08_b2_help",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base2",
      "sourceText": "Якщо ви застрягнете, сніговик може допомогти!",
      "sourceEnText": "If you get stuck, the snowman can help!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_fr08_b2_help.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 3736,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:41:10Z",
      "textHash": "c4cc5db2405065ba727bc0b89eeb180a0a97995b5333f2b6494912cf6663165a"
    },
    {
      "key": "fr08_marmot_2",
      "nodeTitle": "marmot",
      "sourceText": "Я сплю всю зиму під снігом. Це називається зимова сплячка!",
      "sourceEnText": "I sleep all winter under the snow. This is called hibernation!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_fr08_marmot_2.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 4389,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:41:50Z",
      "textHash": "3a005cee42457fa0a8658203665c013a13f4df1231a1b6ebcfc08048afb39593"
    },
    {
      "key": "fr08_marmot_3",
      "nodeTitle": "marmot",
      "sourceText": "Я люблю їсти альпійські квіти та траву. Ням!",
      "sourceEnText": "I love eating alpine flowers and grass. Yum!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_fr08_marmot_3.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 3605,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:41:51Z",
      "textHash": "d083c4bf66cf888d0f1b5a367af14974d84fc6426396d8d199ee078b90757b7d"
    },
    {
      "key": "fr08_marmot_4",
      "nodeTitle": "marmot",
      "sourceText": "Не звертайте на мене уваги, я просто засмагаю на цьому теплому камені.",
      "sourceEnText": "Don't mind me, I'm just sunbathing on this warm rock.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_fr08_marmot_4.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 5172,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:41:52Z",
      "textHash": "c4538376a56a4b65eed6a83878b54e9cb7f199429f20e3f63e9e84a8560fa097"
    },
    {
      "key": "keep_looking",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base2",
      "sourceText": "Продовжуйте шукати. Нам все ще потрібне все спорядження.",
      "sourceEnText": "Keep looking. We still need all the gear.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_keep_looking.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "yaroslava",
